Package controller

Holds all the controllers, that control the layout of the app, and the app entry point Launcher
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ChooseMidiDevice
    Controller controls the choose midi device, and other options screen.
    GameArea
    This controller represents the layout of the game area, the screen where the game will be played.
    Launcher
    Entry point of the app.
    Main
    This is the start screen's controller.
